🖼RINASCIMENTO🖼 “Consciousness expresses itself through creation. This world we live in is the dance of the creator. Dancers come and go in the twinkling of an eye but the dance lives on. On many an occasion when I am dancing, I have felt touched by something sacred.In those moments, I felt my spirit soar and become one with everything that exists. 
I become the stars and the moon. I become the lover and the beloved. I become the victor and the vanquished. I become the master and the slave. I become the singer and the song. I become the knower and the known. I keep on dancing then it is the eternal 
dance or creation. The creator and creation merge into one wholeness of joy. I keep on dancing...and dancing...and dancing. Until there is only...the dance.”

[17.1.17••17.1.19] 🕊"One thing you can always count on is that hearts change." - unnamed prince - Howl’s Moving Castle🕊

2 years ago in one day, my life changed and from that moment I never felt the same, without knowing I got myself into a project that in a night changed my point on all I knew till then, about people, about love, myself and the world itself. I had not thought that going to know the truth it would have hurt me so much, and I have to thank those who understood it, who listened to my story and made me come back to
smile. For months I went on sets with a voice in my head: "Why are you here? you should be somewhere else filming & living  your own truth" and the answer is that maybe I didn’t had the courage, strength, believing yet. It will happen? It will happen. Now all i can say is JUST LOVE , no matter what, JUST LOVE & SMILE,  we are so lucky but sometimes we do not even realize it. JUST BE HAPPY and everything will happen. ❤️ LUCA, 32, A HAPPY GUY. Still believing and always will.

🇮🇹🦜✌🏻#LaTerrazzaÈVeritá✌🏿🦜🇮🇹Today one of my best assistant is leaving for a new adventure in NYC. At first arriving in the office I felt lost, having a “Giornata Particolare” then I started working on a new project I opened a folder and found something my team prepared before holidays, and gave me a new restart. I found a part of my life, and a quote that reminded me the most important thing I’ve learned on the way: SMILE. I never post what i did in the past, but today i felt to share what inspired me and what, then, we made happen. Because History repeats itself but long the way you have to surround yourself with friends and smiles that will give you the power to do everything and face every changing moments. When I was young films were my best friends, then making films i made many true friends and this is the best part of every project. Good Luck Giulia, as I told you yesterday: “The American Dream”, isn’t a place but something inside all of us and with happiness all is possible, duable, relatable. #RIDEREwithNoFilters 🕊🌈🎬✈️🎡🦅 ❤️KING ETTORE SCOLA and his power of FREEDOM ❤️

🎼🎡🦜#$crivendœti🦜🎡🎼 •”Siamo stanchi di diventare giovani seri,
o contenti per forza, o criminali, o nevrotici:
vogliamo ridere, essere innocenti, aspettare
qualcosa dalla vita, chiedere, ignorare.
Non vogliamo essere subito già così sicuri.

che m’hai insegnato ciò che allegri e
feroci
gli uomini imparano bambini,

le piccole cose in cui la grandezza
della vita in pace si scopre, come
andare duri e pronti nella ressa

delle strade, rivolgersi a un altro uomo
senza tremare, non vergognarsi
di guardare il denaro contato

con pigre dita dal fattorino
che suda contro le facciate in corsa
in un colore eterno d’estate;

a difendermi, a offendere, ad avere
il mondo davanti agli occhi e non
soltanto in cuore, a capire

che pochi conoscono le passioni
in cui io sono vissuto:
che non mi sono fraterni, eppure sono

fratelli proprio nell’avere
passioni di uomini
che allegri, inconsci, interi

vivono di esperienze
ignote a me. Stupenda e misera
città che mi hai fatto fare

esperienza di quella vita
ignota: fino a farmi scoprire
ciò che, in ognuno, era il mondo.”
